emotes.msg: Very well, you may start my challenges over from scratch.
I see you've completed my little challenge for you in the Colosseum.  Well done.
For your next challenge, travel deep into the Obsidian Plains and defeat the Shadow of Aerbax. Once you have done so, bring his mask shard to me instead of anyone else.
I wish to study its craftsmanship, manufacture and corruption. There may be something there that can assist in the removal of the threat here.
Your next challenge is one of empowerment. To continue infusing magics into the Paragon Gems, I will need an infusion of Luminance from you.
I am running low on Infused Amber with which to forge your gems. Your next task is to bring me 100 Infused Ambers, so we may continue.
On far Freebooter Isle, there is an old Deru. It has come under attack by one of the corrupted Sclavi, known as Tchk'Tain the Tender. Find him, slay him, and bring his head.
Be warned, he is an elusive one, and sometimes difficult to find. Patience will be your ally in hunting him.

Deep in the desert is the Lost City of Neftet, where the brothers of the A'nekshen Guardians suffer in captivity. Bring me 1,000 A'nekshay Tokens from that place, so they may be returned to their people.
I see that you have recently slain the Mu-miyah Slave Master, which was my challenge for you. Well done.
Your next challenge is one of empowerment. To continue infusing magics into the Paragon Gems, I will need an infusion of Luminance from you.
I am running low on Infused Amber with which to forge your gems. Your next task is to bring me 100 Infused Ambers, so we may continue.
Seek entrance into Lord Mhoire's Tomb, in the graveyard in the Direlands, and defeat Lord Cynreft Mhoire. Inside his chest you will find his signet ring. Bring it to me.
Deep in the Direlands is a place known as the Graveyard of Despair, where old House Mhoire fell. Bring me 1,000 Ancient Mhoire Coins from that place.
Deep inside Mhoire Castle you will find the Shade of Lord Rytheran, who used the Book of Eibhil to destroy all of House Mhoire, Slay him and bring his ring to me.
Your next challenge is one of empowerment. To continue infusing magics into the Paragon Gems, I will need an infusion of Luminance from you.
I am running low on Infused Amber with which to forge your gems. Your next task is to bring me 200 Infused Ambers, so we may continue.
Seek the ghost of Lady Tairla Mhoire, in the graveyard in the Direlands, and defeat her. Inside her chest you will find her signet ring. Bring it to me.
In Northern Osteth lies the lair of the Paradox-touched Olthoi Queen. Her children swarm over the surface above her lair.
Bring me 1,000 Small Olthoi Venom Sacs from the Paradox-touched Olthoi there, so I may study the strange magical corruptions used upon them.
In Northern Osteth lies the lair of the Paradox-touched Olthoi Queen. Enter her lair, slay her, and bring me a shard of her carapace as proof.
Your next challenge is one of empowerment. To continue infusing magics into the Paragon Gems, I will need an infusion of Luminance from you.
I am running low on Infused Amber with which to forge your gems. Your next task is to bring me 200 Infused Ambers, so we may continue.
In the ancient Colosseum there is a challenge to defeat a creature called the "Thunder Chicken". Slay this mighty beast and bring me it's token as proof.
In the northern Direlands are strange creatures called Gear Knights. Bring me 1,000 of their Ornate Gear Markers so I may study their construction techniques.

In the northern Direlands are strange creatures called Gear Knights. One of them is known as the Iron Blade Overseer. Defeat him and bring his Aetherium Core here, so I may better understand these strange creatures.
Your next challenge is one of empowerment.  To continue infusing magics into the Paragon Gems, I will need an infusion of Luminance from you.
I am running low on Infused Amber with which to forge your gems. Your next task is to bring me 200 Infused Ambers, so we may continue.
This may seem a bit odd, but your next task is to bring me 100 Corrupted Ambers, which can be gathered from the Viridian Chasm, below.
I wish to experiment with more efficient ways to cleanse the amber, and what is left will help fuel the creation of more Paragon Gems for you.
The ancient Colosseum uses a strange currency to reward those who participate in its games.  Bring me 1,000 Colosseum Coins to complete your next challenge.

Deep in the Oubliette under House Mhoire one can find a thing called the Spectral Fountain. Gather a Corrupted Amber from the Viridian Chasm below, and place it into the Spectral Fountain. Return to me with whatever result you find.
Your next challenge is one of empowerment. To continue infusing magics into the Paragon Gems, I will need an infusion of Luminance from you.
I am running low on Infused Amber with which to forge your gems. Your next task is to bring me 300 Infused Ambers, so we may continue.
Enter the Colosseum once again. This time, defeat the one known as The Master and bring me his token.
In the Obsidian Plains hides one of the Lothus Virindi known as the Curator of Torment. Defeat the vile thing and bring me the shard of his mask as proof.
Your next task is to bring me 200 Corrupted Ambers from the Viridian Chasm below.
My last experiments were promising, but incomplete. Also, as before, what is left will help fuel the creation of more Paragon Gems for you...
Your next challenge is one of empowerment.  To continue infusing magics into the Paragon Gems, I will need an infusion of Luminance from you.
I am running low on Infused Amber with which to forge your gems. Your next task is to bring me 300 Infused Ambers, so we may continue.

In the forests of Northern Osteth lies the spectral Fortress of Hoshino Kei. One of her generals, General Idah can sometimes be found inspecting his forces in the haunted towns around the outside of the fortress itself.
Your next challenge is to complete 30 'Legendary Quests' and then return to me.
And I see you have already proven yourself in this challenge. Well done.
Enter the colosseum and defeat the challenge of Gladiator Diemos. Once he is defeated, bring his token to me.
Your next challenge is one of empowerment.  To continue infusing magics into the Paragon Gems, I will need an infusion of Luminance from you.
I am running low on Infused Amber with which to forge your gems. Your next task is to bring me 300 Infused Ambers, so we may continue.

In the forests of Northern Osteth lies the spectral Fortress of Hoshino Kei. One of her generals, General Nobanuga can sometimes be found inspecting his forces in the haunted towns around the outside of the fortress itself.
He is elusive, so be patient. Once you have slain him, bring me his shattered helm as proof.
In the place known as the Gauntlet there is a challenge to defeat a Marionette known as Tremb'Orh. Defeat it and bring its token to me as proof.
In the forests of Northern Osteth lies the spectral Fortress of Hoshino Kei.  Find the entrance to her deepest sanctum and slay her. Once you have, bring her Mirror Shard to me.
Your next challenge is one of empowerment.  To continue infusing magics into the Paragon Gems, I will need an infusion of Luminance from you.
I am running low on Infused Amber with which to forge your gems. Your next task is to bring me 400 Infused Ambers, so we may continue.

Your next challenge may be the most difficult yet.  Within the Viridian Rise, four Elite Guardians stalk the land.  Defeat one of these Elite Guardians and bring proof of their fall to me.  They have been driven by the Great Tree's pain, and their defeat will help set them free.
Your next challenge is to complete 40 'Legendary Quests' and then return to me.
And I see you have already proven yourself in this challenge. Well done.
And I see you have already proven yourself in this challenge. Well done.
In the place known as the Gauntlet there is a challenge to defeat a Doll known as Holcha. Defeat it and bring its token to me as proof.
Your next challenge is the last one of empowerment. To continue infusing magics into the final Paragon Gems, I will need the largest infusion of Luminance from you yet.
The ritual to empower the final Paragon Gem is a costly one. To craft your final imbue, I will need 500 Infused Ambers for the ritual.
When you have given the ambers to me, we will begin.

I am known as Summercrown, and I am the Master of the Amber Forge.
I use the energies of the forge, along with the blessings of the Deru, to craft empowerments for the Guardians of the Deru, scattered throughout Auberean.
The Deru have agreed that those who reach me in this place and aid us with the corruption that spreads here are worthy of my blessings.
To honor their wishes, I have forged their blessings into the Paragon Weapon Gems. These gems will empower the weapon of your choice with the blessings of the Paragon.
These blessings grow as the imbued weapon gains in experience, and as you complete my challenges, the gems I will craft for you will increase your Paragon Weapon's capacity to learn.

There are 50 challenges to fully imbue a Paragon Weapon, and 50 tiers of learning they can gain the imbue gems I craft. Every time you complete one of my challenges, you will be rewarded with a gem that will increase the level of your Paragon Weapon by 1.
Your first challenge is a simple and practical one. Bring me 100 Infused Ambers, so I may use them to forge the first few gems you will be earning.
Your next task is simple. Travel to the Colosseum, defeat it, and return to me.
Don't worry about those challenges that exist alongside the actual Colosseum. This challenge is only for the timed arena.
In the Lost City of Neftet, the brothers of the A'nekshen Guardians suffer in captivity. Seek entrance into the Sand Temple, and destroy the Mu-miyah Slave Master.
Once the Slave Master is dead and the A'nekshay are freed, return to me.
